Clean up old projects automatically
---

As a administrator,
I want to clean up all old projects,
So that the system doesn't get cluttered with old projects.

---

-- Viewing old projects
Given
	I am on the admin dashboard,
When
	I click on 'clean up old projects...',
Then
	I am presented with a list of old projects (e.g. > 180 days old).


-- Cleaning up all old projects
Given
	I am viewing a list of old projects,
When
	I click 'Remove all',
Then
	All old projects are removed.
